(print "║                                                              ║")
(print "║  This is not science fiction. Every component is real:      ║")
(print "║                                                              ║")
(print "║  ① Neural LLM compression (Nature MI, 2025):               ║")
(print "║    2-3× better than best traditional compressors            ║")
