(print "║                                                              ║")
(print "║  ② DNA virtual address space (Science Advances, 2021):     ║")
(print "║    >60 PB addressable per cm³                               ║")
(print "║    We virtualize: content hash → DNA coord → tiny index     ║")
(print "║                                                              ║")
(print "║  ③ 7D optical encoding (this document + extensions):        ║")
(print "║    2D space + time + 3 colors + 4 phases + 8 t-slots        ║")
